                "invention-title": [
                    "Experimental device and method for simulating soil water replenishment by underground water evaporation",
                    "一种模拟地下水蒸发补给土壤水的实验装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides an experimental device and method for simulating underground water evaporation and soil water replenishment, the bottom end of a soil column casing in the device is arranged on a chassis, and the top end of the soil column casing is of an open structure. The water-permeable plate is located in the soil column casing and close to a preset height of the chassis, so that an oxyhydrogen isotope solution storage area is formed between the chassis and the water-permeable plate, and a supply inlet is formed in the upper part of the oxyhydrogen isotope solution storage area. A soil water saturation area, a water transmission area and a soil root area with preset heights are sequentially arranged in the soil column cylinder from bottom to top from the position of the water permeable plate. According to the device and the method provided by the invention, the hydrogen and oxygen isotope liquid is adopted to simulate underground water, tracing research is carried out on soil water supplied by underground water evaporation, different partitions are arranged for the soil column, and influence factors of plant roots on the soil water supplied by the underground water are considered; therefore, the migration height of the underground water, the supply effect of the underground water on soil water and the threshold value of the diving depth which can be utilized by plants can be accurately judged."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种模拟地下水蒸发补给土壤水的实验装置及方法，其中，该装置中的土柱筒的底端布置在底盘上，土柱筒的顶端为敞口结构。透水板位于土柱筒内靠近底盘预设高度处使得底盘与透水板之间形成氢氧同位素溶液储备区，氢氧同位素溶液储备区上部设有补给入口。土柱筒内从透水板位置开始从下到上依次设有预设高度的土壤水饱和区、水分传输区和土壤根区。本发明提供的装置及方法，采用了氢氧同位素液体模拟地下水，对地下水蒸发补给土壤水进行示踪研究，并且对土柱设置了不同的分区，考虑了植物根系对地下水补给土壤水的影响因素，从而非常精准地判断地下水的运移高度及对土壤水的补给作用和植物可以利用到潜水深度的阈值。"
                }
            ]
